{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468090/extras/wanderdawnMainArt_EN.png?t=1738008880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore various worlds in a hack-and-slash action game - In a world ravaged by an unknown disaster, face various monsters with the diverse weapons you find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468090/extras/\u30af\u30e9\u30d5\u30a1\u30f3\u8cc7\u6599_\u30b9\u30c8\u30fc\u30ea\u30fc_EN.png?t=1738008880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25aa\ufe0eExplore the post apocalyptic world and take on powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25aa\ufe0eThe \u201cWorld Class\u201d bosses are so huge that they cover the entire world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25aa\ufe0eDifferentiated weapons with built-in transformations and gimmicks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25aa\ufe0eFind your own play style by using spiritual devices that allow you to perform a variety of skills such as emergency dodging, firing wires, riding robots, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25aa\ufe0eTravel from town to town in a mysterious world created by a disaster of unknown origin. Explore a fantastical world created by people's memories.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3468090?t=1738008880","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3468090?t=1738008880","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468090/4784782f3e8279e3e2b57297237711e9e84ce6d8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738008880","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/